That&#39;s funny. I heard the same thing about 1000...that in ecology if a
species gets under 1000 they really start to worry about the population. I
don&#39;t think 30 will do it, but I confess I have not read any literature on
it recently.

Anyone else know?

Has anyone done any studies with NEAT on pop size to see what the plot of
pop size vs. fitness looks like?




Cheers,
